### How It Works
1. **Automatic Tracking**: Once deployed to Vercel, Speed Insights automatically:
   - Injects the tracking script at `/_vercel/speed-insights/script.js`
   - Collects Core Web Vitals metrics
   - Sends performance data to Vercel dashboard

2. **Client-Side Only**: The component runs only in the browser and collects real user monitoring (RUM) data

3. **Privacy**: Data collection respects browser privacy settings and Vercel's privacy standards

### Deployment Steps (for reference)
1. Enable Speed Insights on Vercel dashboard for the project
2. Deploy the app to Vercel using `vercel deploy` or Git integration
3. After deployment, the `/_vercel/speed-insights/script.js` endpoint will be available
4. Data will start appearing in the Speed Insights dashboard after user visits

